Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh. Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku duduk di sebelahmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Bagaimana kau tahu ini aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, kau tidak bisa melihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mencium aromamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Endus, endus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, maksudku bukan kau bau!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku mengeluarkan aroma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu! Aku tidak bisa melihat,\Njadi hidung dan telingaku lebih sensitif!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, hidungmu pasti tajam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa mencium bau badanku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Kau sama sekali tidak bau!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat kau, sekarang aku tahu\Nkalau aku punya aroma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, di mana aku sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin cuma kau di dunia ini\Nyang bisa menemukanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku berdebar kencang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berdebar...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau makan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanan Eropa, Tiongkok, atau Jepang?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau alergi sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada restoran tertentu yang kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, aku jarang makan di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit sekali tempat\Nyang pernah kukunjungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa pergi\Nke restoran mana pun yang kau mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Ada restoran yang ingin kucoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya! Di sana! Ayo ke sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan pegang aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai jalan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langkah kakinya tidak stabil...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia ragu akan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Mungkin dia tak tahu mau ke mana,\Ndan sedang mencoba mencarinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Itu semua\Nkarena aku tidak memilih restorannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, maaf sudah merepotkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau mencium aroma\Nyang sangat enak? Ke arah mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadinya aku khawatir jika kita masuk,\Ndan itu tidak sesuai seleramu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah memilih bersamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, terima kasih!\NAku tak sabar mencobanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya aku ke sini,\Njadi aku pesan menu rekomendasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku belum pernah mencium\Nbeberapa aroma ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ini petualangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini petualangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Apa ini sayuran? Rasanya aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ketumbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya\Naku makan bersama rekan kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku berdebar kencang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau makan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak memikirkannya karena fokus\Nsoal pergi ke suatu tempat pertama kali,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi apakah ini dianggap kencan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dia tidak menyebutnya kencan,\Njadi mungkin bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutaruh di piringmu, hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arah jam 12 di piringmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, ini pertama kalinya\Naku makan bersama seorang pria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya berpikir,\Nrasanya ini seperti kencan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah niatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau merasa gugup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu... Sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berpikir, sungguh memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, boleh pinjam tanganmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak terlihat, jadi selalu sulit\Nbagi orang lain untuk mengetahuinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau mungkin bisa tahu,\Nbahkan lewat pakaianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak ingin kau berpikir\Nhanya kau yang gugup malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, jantungmu juga berdebar kencang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak ingin semua orang tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan malam yang menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang restoran ini pilihan yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku juga senang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan pegang aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan antar kau ke stasiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, jantungku masih berdebar kencang\Nkarena yang tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin berbahaya\Njika kau tak pegang erat-erat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, aku bawa tongkat putihku!\NAku akan baik-baik saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak berusaha\Nmembuat jarak di antara kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, aku... Bagaimana mengatakannya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, apakah justru sebaliknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, hapus seringai itu dari wajahmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak bisa menyembunyikannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan\Nmenyembunyikan apa pun darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sebenarnya, aku ingin diketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, aku merasa\Ningin melompat-lompat kecil sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau melompat bersamaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Tolong jangan lakukan itu, Tonome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku akan menekan emosiku untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau izinkan aku\Nmengantarmu dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Tonome dan aku\Nbersenang-senang bersama hari ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Air mandinya sudah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa dia pria yang sangat baik\Nsejak dia mewawancaraiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berbicara\Ndengan nada dan suara yang tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu gerakannya bersih dan halus\Ndari suaranya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome adalah orang yang menyenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau begitulah menurutku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, berhenti! Kalian baru\Nmakan malam sekali! Pelan-pelan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran\Napa yang Tonome pikirkan tentang aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan sebenarnya, aku ingin diketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dia maksud dengan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome adalah manusia tak kasatmata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, orang tidak bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang bisa melihat\Ntidak bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran seperti apa rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, apa kau merasa ingin dilihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku, dilihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... kurasa tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan menjadi diriku\Njika aku terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, apakah kau ingin melihatku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa merasakan kau orang seperti apa,\Ndan menurutku itu sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pemikiran yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, jadi Tonome\Ntidak keberatan dirinya tak terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau tidak terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, itu sepedaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang hilang, pemeriksaan latar belakang,\Npengumpulan bukti,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami tangani semua jenis penyelidikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin membuat janji temu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku akan periksa jadwal\Ndan menghubungimu kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita lihat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang memasang tembok di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang kau sebut tembok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menghalangiku. Mundur lima langkah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menaruh kopi\Ndi sebelah kanan komputermu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarashi, Kikira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:11:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa menurut kalian aku terlihat aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Apa kau sudah menemukan\Norang yang menarik bagimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau secantik biasanya hari ini, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin menceritakan kisah cintamu,\Naku siap mendengarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahmu merah padam! Lucu sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Kau tak pantas mengatakan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku menyentuh rambutmu sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyentuh... rambutku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, kau keberatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak keberatan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa merasakan\Ntangan Tonome mendekat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah. Ada bunga sakura di rambutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah musim semi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh. Terima kasih untuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa sangat malu\Nkarena terlalu tegang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu. Jangan bilang kalau pria itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, sudah hampir waktunya\Nuntuk rapatmu! Mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku akan bawakan dokumennya sebentar lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau tak keberatan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisakah kau memberikan lebih banyak detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia penggoda sejati. Aku ingin pastikan\Ndia serius mau menikah denganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang,\Naku melihat katak yang mengeong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia selingkuh!\NDia bertingkah sangat mencurigakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa hidup selama 80.000 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia lahir bersama dengan galaksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Spesialisasinya adalah membentuk bintang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mampu melakukan\Nperjalanan antarbintang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maaf, tapi bisa berikan informasi\Nsoal penampilan putri kalian yang hilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pupilnya 5 mm lebih besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lengannya 1 cm lebih panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bibirnya 10 persen lebih lembap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Giginya kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah mencatat sebisaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ras mereka\Nmemiliki sedikit variasi sifat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kita menemukannya berdasarkan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kita hanya perlu mencari orang\Nyang mirip dengan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku! Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi manusia tak kasatmata\Nmembuat pekerjaan ini jadi lebih mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia langsung pergi ke kantor\Nsetelah menyelesaikan panggilan penjualan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, aku menunggu\Ndia menyelesaikan pekerjaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi manusia tak kasatmata\Nitu tidak mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau terlihat sangat bahagia hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu dengan Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Ti-Tidak, tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mendengarkan novel ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Mendengarkan... novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mendengarkan buku audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin mencoba mendengarkan juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa berhenti mendengarkan\Nnovel romansa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka makan malam saat berkencan,\Ndan sekuntum mawar mendekatkan mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ini novel romansa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, bagaimana caramu?\NAku tak bisa mendengar sepatah kata pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku sudah mendengarkannya\Nsejak masih kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:15:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, Jarashi,\Nkau adalah manusia monster, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar seharusnya kau memiliki\Ntelinga dan hidung yang sensitif.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, biasanya aku tidak seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Tonome, kau di sini?\NAku tidak menyadarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak sepenuhnya\Ntak terlihat saat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbeda ketika aku sedang fokus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, hanya ketika kau sedang fokus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang, aku mendengarnya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di laporan investigasi Tonome dan Kikira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau ada kesulitan dengan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika fokus, aku akan membereskan\Napa pun yang kau butuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, aku tak perlu membereskan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bisakah kau meminjamkan\Nmatamu sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, aku tak bisa tahu\Nangka di tanda terima ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tintanya tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang hal seperti itu terjadi.\NBerapa yang tertulis di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini 1.600 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, di tanda terimanya tertulis\N"Churun ​​Manusia Monster Ukuran Besar".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini barang belanjaanmu, 'kan, Jarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kebetulan menemukannya\Nsaat mengawal klien.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat sulit ditemukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harganya juga sangat murah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangnya, itu tidak dihitung\Nsebagai pengeluaran bisnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Tidak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.\NMereka tidak membuat Churun untuk manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu masalahnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat! Aku harus pergi sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya! Aku meletakkan ponsel\Ndan penyuara telingamu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di sebelah kiri komputermu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati di jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai nanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sudah agak malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Tonome lama?\NSeharusnya dia sudah kembali sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Tidak ada orang di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, apakah kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terluka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau terluka?! Di mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tidak memberitahuku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, tunjukkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Aku tidak terluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, Jarashi membawakan kotak P3K untukku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa kau yang membutuhkannya,\Nbukan aku, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa bersembunyi darimu\Ndengan menjadi tidak terlihat, Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengalami sedikit masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melaporkan temuanku\Ntentang penyelidikan perselingkuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berani selingkuh dariku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kau menyewa detektif?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Jelas kau yang salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sudah, sudah.\N- Menyelinap seperti tikus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetap tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ikut campur!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencoba menengahi\Ndan terluka saat melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mengerikan! Apa kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, klien sadar dan menenangkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang selalu penasaran
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana segala sesuatu\Nyang keluar dari tubuhku menjadi terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah, manusia tak kasatmata\Njuga bisa berdarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru kali ini aku melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang sangat terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertanya apakah kau tidak apa-apa!\NKau terluka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau mengkhawatirkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lukaku tak terlihat,\Njadi aku tak bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ragu luka ini parah.\NMungkin aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi darahnya lebih banyak dari dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mu-Mungkin? Jika kau mengeluarkan\Nbanyak darah, kau bisa mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perdarahannya tidak terlalu banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apakah ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm. Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau menahan kasanya\Nselagi aku menempelkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu harus berkata apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut membuatmu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi anehnya aku merasa bahagia.\NBahkan rasanya menggelitik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku menggelitikmu?\NHaruskah aku memegangnya secara berbeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku cukup mudah geli.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau ingin aku menggelitikmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tolong jangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Yang lainnya sudah pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kupikir mereka sudah selesai\Nuntuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau akan pergi sekarang, Yako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Bagaimana denganmu, Tonome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku harus menulis laporan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau belum akan pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Pekerjaanku tertunda,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan luka ini tidak terlalu parah\Nhingga bisa mengalihkan perhatianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm. Berarti dia bekerja lembur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti belum istirahat\Nsama sekali hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku akan tetap di sini\Ndan memesan perlengkapan kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau tidak perlu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em... setelah aku selesai memesannya,\Nkau mau istirahat denganku sejenak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Mari kita\Nistirahat sejenak sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Bagaimana dengan pekerjaanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mengurusnya nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi terima kasih, Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membuatkan teh untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah ini teh hitam baru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini teh herbal campuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membelinya karena penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harum sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang kau menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome mengajakku makan malam sebelumnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu akan menjadi\Nyang terakhir kalinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat berharap bisa berkencan lagi\Ndengan Tonome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nkenapa aku tidak mengajaknya saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tapi itu mungkin\Nakan membuatnya repot...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak! Ini pertanyaan\Ntentang keberanianku sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako, omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau ingin\Nmakan malam bersama hari ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! A-A-Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, boleh aku mengajakmu\Nuntuk jalan-jalan berikutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukan toko tempat kita bisa\Nmembuat teh campuran sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mengajakmu ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.04,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku menerima ajakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu terburu-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari tentukan tanggalnya dulu.
